)%20told%20me%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20jealous.%20I%20want%20to%20do%20that.%20How%20did%20you%20swing%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22349dd71e-1365-4086-82e3-e5761434559c%5C%22%3EI%20had%20hit%20a%20breaking%20point%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20be%20alone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-favorite-thanksgiving-is-the-one-i-spent-alone-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eduring%20the%20holidays%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20slowly%20at%20first%20and%20then%20all%20at%20once.%20I'd%20hit%20a%20breaking%20point%20that%20most%20parents%2C%20especially%20moms%2C%20are%20all%20too%20familiar%20with.%20But%20the%20moment%20I%20toyed%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20staying%20back%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20quiet%2C%20clean%2C%20empty%20house%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20it.%20It%20was%20all%20I%20could%20think%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221647%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20at%20the%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6961599364858d02d21817c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221238%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20spouse%20was%20supportive%20of%20her%20taking%20time%20off.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20broached%20the%20topic%2C%20gently%2C%20with%20my%20husband%2C%20who%20couldn't%20have%20been%20more%20supportive%20and%20emphatic.%20%26quot%3BYou%20%3Cem%3Eshould%3C%2Fem%3E%20take%20a%20few%20days%20away!%26quot%3B%20But%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20%3Cem%3Eaway%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20home%20%3Cem%3Ealone%3C%2Fem%3E.%20That%20was%20the%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20days%20ticked%20closer%20to%20The%20Big%20Departure%2C%20people%20asked%20me%20when%20Jeff%20and%20the%20kids%20were%20leaving.%20%26quot%3BWednesday%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20ask%20when%2C%20specifically%2C%26quot%3B%20I'd%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20explained%20to%20the%20kids%20that%20I%20needed%20some%20a