t%20Grok%20after%20some%20used%20it%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grok-remove-clothes-ai-images-women-minors-backlash-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigitally%20undress%20real%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20photos%2C%20and%20then%20post%20them%20to%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20authorities%20told%20Politico%20this%20month%20that%20they%20will%20investigate%20sexually%20explicit%20deepfakes%20generated%20by%20Grok.%20And%20the%20Indian%20government%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20X's%20chief%20compliance%20representative%20in%20the%20country%20that%20Grok%20is%20being%20%26quot%3Bmisused%20by%20users%26quot%3B%20to%20generate%20%26quot%3Bimages%20or%20videos%20of%20women%20in%20a%20derogatory%20or%20vulgar%20manner%20in%20order%20to%20indecently%20denigrate%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20asked%20X%20to%20conduct%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20technical%2C%20procedural%2C%20and%20governance-level%20review%26quot%3B%20and%20remove%20content%20violating%20the%20country's%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfcom%2C%20the%20UK's%20communications%20regulator%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bmade%20urgent%20contact%20with%20X%20and%20xAI%20to%20understand%20what%20steps%20they%20have%20taken%20to%20comply%20with%20their%20legal%20duties%20to%20protect%20users%20in%20the%20UK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20US%20senators%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20asked%20Apple%20and%20Google%20to%20remove%20X%20and%20Grok%20from%20their%20app%20stores%20over%20the%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTurning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20X's%20egregious%20behavior%20would%20make%20a%20mockery%20of%20your%20moderation%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senators%20write%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BIndeed%2C%20not%20taking%20action%20would%20undermine%20your%20claims%20in%20public%20and%20in%20court%20that%20your%20app%20stores%20offer%20a%20safer%20user%20experience%20than%20letting%