.com%2Fworking-mom-wrote-letters-to-teachers-made-difference-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20pick-ups%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20drop-offs.%20And%20your%20go-to%20phone%20call%20when%20your%20babysitter%20is%20sick%20one%20hour%20before%20your%20anniversary%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20best%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%20I%20wouldn't%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20lives%20in%20Haslett%2C%20Michigan%20%E2%80%94%201%2C891%20miles%20away%20from%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-back-to-hometown-after-avoiding-love-living-portland-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20in%20Portland%2C%20Oregon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She's%20the%20only%20living%20grandmother%20to%20my%20two%20daughters%2C%206%20and%208%2C%20and%20their%20only%20grandfather%20is%20close%2C%20but%20at%2085%2C%20his%20mobility%20is%20limited.%20There%20are%20no%20pop-ins%2C%20drop-offs%2C%20or%20backups%2C%20and%20they%20lose%20out%20on%20that%20daily%2C%20in-person%20bonding%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20other%20families%20are%20in%20the%20same%20situation.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.demographic-research.org%2Farticles%2Fvolume%2F52%2F34%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Cornell%20researchers%20found%20that%20about%20one%20in%20seven%20children%20lives%20500%20miles%20or%20more%20from%20their%20grandparents.%20Despite%20the%20distance%2C%20we've%20found%20ways%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%2C%20making%20it%20feel%20like%20Grandma%20is%20always%20near.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226896ef17-b469-479a-a61d-809cefc29f5c%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20challenges%20to%20living%20far%20from%20Grandma%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20distance%20means%20Grandma%20misses%20all%20the%20fun%20firsts.%20She's%20missed%20first%20steps%2C%20first%20words%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fback-to-school-season-more-stressful-for-mom-than-kids-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20days%20of%20school%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20it's%20not%20just%20big%20moments.%20When%20she's%20back%20in%20town%2C%20they%20suddenly%20know%20how%20to%20do%20things%20like%20brush%20their%20own%20hair%2C%20tie%20shoelaces%2C%20and%20buckle%20seatbelts.%20She%20missed%20those%20little%20wins%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20harder%20to%20pass%20down%20family%20traditions%20and%20history%2C%20though%20we've%20still%20found%20a%20way%20to%20give%20our%20kids%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging.%20Grandma's%20great-aunt's%20German%20'city%20chicken'%20recipe%2C%20which%20is%20breaded%20veal%20or%20pork%20on%20a%20stick%20(it's%20good%2C%20I%20swear!)%2C%20tells%20my%20kids%20where%20they%20come%20from.%20The%20bedtime%20lullaby%20she%20learned%20from%20her%20own%20grandmother%20shows%20nurturing%20runs%20in%20the%20family.%20The%20black-and-white%20picture%20on%20Grandma's%20shelf%2C%20filled%20with%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20who%20look%20like%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20my%20daughters%20say%2C%20lets%20them%20know%20they're%20not%20alone%20in%20this%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20daughters%20with%20his%20mom%20in%20Oregon%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695d44a304eda4732f2e8dfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20family%20lives%20almost%202%2C000%20miles%20from%20his%20mother%2C%20but%20his%20daughters%20are%20still%20close%20with%20their%20grandmother.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brendan%20Knapp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236f9ab42-151a-4af1-b34e-dbeb734514b0%5C%22%3EWe've%20worked%20hard%20to%20make%20it%20feel%20like%20she%20lives%20next%20door%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20couple%20of%20rituals%20that%20help%20us%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-grandparents-live-far-away-facetime-visit-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay%20connected%20in%20between%20visits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20our%20daughters%20were%20babies%20and%20toddlers%2C%20Grandma%20would%20chat%20from%20a%20screen%20while%20they%20splashed%20around%20during%20baths.%20She'd%20talk%20about%20her%20day%2C%20ask%20about%20theirs%2C%20and%20tell%20stories.%20My%20girls%20would%20get%20so%20excited%20to%20hang%20out%20with%20Grandma.%20As%20soon%20as%20I'd%20tell%20them%2C%20%26quot%3BGrandma's%20calling%2C%26quot%3B%20they'd%20run%20for%20the%20tub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20Sunday%2C%20for%20several%20years%20now%2C%20she%20reads%20to%20my%20girls%20for%20an%20hour%20through%20an%20app%20called%20Readeo.%20It%20features%20hundreds%20of%20books%20that%20they%20can%20navigate%20together%2C%20and%20they%20can%20see%20each%20other%20on%20the%20video%20screen.%20And%20once%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaughter-struggling-to-read-she-needed-glasses-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20learning%20to%20read%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20got%20to%20fill%20me%20in%20on%20some%20of%20their%20firsts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db540765-7ae1-4cdc-8d53-b1f9d6e76197%5C%22%3EOur%20in-person%20visits%20mean%20even%20more%20these%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20non-stop%20flights%20from%20Detroit%20to%20Portland%2C%20which%20allow%20Grandma%20to%20attend%20ballet%20recitals%2C%20spend%20Christmas%20mornings%20with%20us%2C%20and%20go%20with%20us%20to%20the%20Oregon%20coast.%20She%20comes%20our%20way%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20and%20we%20head%20her%20way%20once%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20visit%20her%2C%20it's%20special.%20My%20girls%20love%20to%20stay%20at%20her%20home.%20They%20snuggle%20under%20blankets%20that%20smell%20like%20her%2C%20ask%20about%20where%20her%20art%20comes%20from%2C%20and%20fall%20into%20her%20routine.%20Waking%20up%20is%20an%20intimate%20pocket%20of%20time%20they%20share%20before%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20awake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure